_sText: De_operation_groundhog v1.0 --------------------------------- Special thanks to chizbone for the custom nav file & place painting the radar. An underground facility that servers no real purpose. The terrorist's objective is to bomb one of the two lifts, leading to the surface. Reason? Because the CT's love their lifts and won't share it with anyone. Spawn-points: 32 Recommended players: 16~20 Use teamwork to boost others to higher ground to give your team the advantage.
